1. "Kako da povezemo naše *mozga* i ostanemo zdravi?" (How to connect our brains and stay healthy?) 
2. "On je poput *mozga* oko koga se vrti sve." (He is like the brain around which everything revolves.) 
3. "Ona je sposobna da poveže svoje *mozge* i da misli kreativno." (She is capable of connecting her brains and thinking creatively.) 
4. "Zašto je potrebno da se stimulišu *mozga* tokom starosti?" (Why is it necessary to stimulate brains during old age?) 
5. "Kako da se aktiviraju *mozge* i razviju nove sposobnosti?" (How to activate brains and develop new abilities?)